<plot>"Tomorrow Never Comes?" is a comedy/action film. A newscaster has dismal ratings, and is on the verge of being fired. Mike, along with his camera-man, concocts a plan and makes fake terrorist news broadcasts. They broadcast these worldwide. However,in a round about way, Mike finds himself working with a North Korean terrorist and ex-KGB agents. He is pursued By the CIA, FBI, US Department of state agents and even Canadian Intelligence! the lines between reality and fantasy blur for the Mike as the film progresses Is it reality, or just a dream? Featuring music by New Jersey recording artist Art "Flesh" Gordon and artwork by Anita Bruckert.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?101675</url></doc>
